comment: /**  * Set the default value for HTML escaping,  * to be put into the current PageContext.  */
code: /**  * Set the default value for HTML escaping,  * to be put into the current PageContext.  */ public void setDefaultHtmlEscape(boolean defaultHtmlEscape) {     this.defaultHtmlEscape = defaultHtmlEscape. }
@Override protected int doStartTagInternal() throws JspException {     getRequestContext().setDefaultHtmlEscape(this.defaultHtmlEscape).     return EVAL_BODY_INCLUDE. }
